column5: Heading up to Nestor Falls in 3 weeks and wondering about highway 71 conditions south of there
Will be heading up that way on Wednesday 9/7, will let you know. I'm curious about the construction at the 11 and 71 intersection, it shouldn't be a big deal.

So, heading West out of Fort Francis Hwy 11 is down to one lane for a short distance with flag men, about a 5-10 minute delay. At the Hwy 11 & 71 intersection they were finishing up repaving 71 from that intersection for about 5 or 6 miles. Only delay was going North from that intersection for a mile or 2 it was down to 1 lane with a flag man. Wasn't bad at all. Buy the time you go up it might be completed.
